On the fifth day of my internship, I focused on planning the next stages of the virtual piano project.
The development process to be followed after the procurement of the required hardware was
reviewed, and the sequence of the project tasks was determined.

As part of this planning process, I evaluated how the image processing applications would be 
integrated with the ESP32-CAM, identified the software components required for the system, and 
planned the overall structure of the machine learning applications that will be incorporated into the 
project in the later stages. In addition, the possible technical requirements of the project were 
considered, and an appropriate development approach was established.

By the end of the day, the project roadmap had been finalized, and the necessary preparations for the 
implementation phase following the arrival of the hardware had been completed.
